1. META


    file_name: D35.gif

    duration: ~2.0 sec

    loop: yes / no / seamless

    fps: 30

    resolution: 1920x1080

    format: gif / mp4


2. SCENE


    background_color: "#1a2b2e" (dark teal-grey)

    canvas_orientation: landscape

    camera: static

    objects_count: 7

    main_subject: Rounded rectangle icon with central diamond in top-left quadrant


3. OBJECTS

Object A: Main Icon Container


    type: shape

    shape: rounded_rect

    size_relative: ~15% height of canvas

    position: top-left quadrant

    fill: "#d9d9d9" (light grey)

    stroke: "#FF8800" (orange), width ~6px

    corner_radius: ~15px


Object B: Central Diamond


    type: shape

    shape: rotated_square (45°)

    size_relative: ~60% of main icon

    position: center of main icon

    fill: "#FFFFFF" (white)

    stroke: none


Object C: Internal Symbol


    type: shape/text

    shape: custom_path (interlocking N/Z geometric pattern)

    size_relative: ~40% of central diamond

    position: center of central diamond

    fill: "#000000" (black)

    stroke: none


Object D: Status Bar


    type: shape

    shape: rectangle

    size_relative: ~80% width of main icon, thin height

    position: bottom edge of main icon's light field

    fill: "#FF8800" (orange)

    stroke: none


Object E: Checkmark Box


    type: shape

    shape: rounded_rect

    size_relative: ~20% of main icon

    position: top-right corner overlapping main icon

    fill: "#FF8800" (orange)

    stroke: "#FFFFFF" (white checkmark)


Object F: Expanding Diamond Outline


    type: shape

    shape: rotated_square (45°)

    size_relative: starts at central diamond size, grows to ~150% of main icon

    position: center, expands outward

    fill: none

    stroke: "#FFFFFF" (white), width 2-3px, fades with expansion


Object G: Header Line with Moving Dash


    type: shape

    shape: line/rectangle

    size_relative: full width, thin height

    position: top of dark panel, above icon

    fill: "#3a4a4e" (subtle grey)

    stroke: none


4. ANIMATION

Animation 1: Icon Pop Effect


    target_property: Scale Transform

    keyframes:

        0.0s: scale=100%

        0.1s: scale=105-110%

        0.3s: scale=100%


    easing: easeOutBack

    loop: cycle

    direction: in-out


Animation 2: Expanding Diamond Pulse


    target_property: Scale + Opacity + Stroke Width

    keyframes:

        0.0s: scale=1.0, opacity=100%, width=2px

        0.3s: scale=1.5, opacity=0%, width=4px

        1.5s: scale=1.0, opacity=100%, width=2px


    easing: easeOut

    loop: cycle

    direction: one-way (expands and fades)


Animation 3: Bloom/Flash Effect


    target_property: Glow Intensity + Opacity

    keyframes:

        0.0s: glow=0, opacity=0%

        0.05s: glow=100%, opacity=100% (peak)

        0.4s: glow=0, opacity=0%


    easing: easeOut

    loop: cycle

    direction: one-way


Animation 4: Light Sweep/Glint


    target_property: Position + Opacity

    keyframes:

        0.0s: position=top-left corner of symbol, opacity=0%

        0.2s: position=bottom-right corner of symbol, opacity=100%

        0.4s: position=bottom-right corner of symbol, opacity=0%


    easing: linear

    loop: cycle

    direction: one-way


Animation 5: Header Dash Translate


    target_property: Position X

    keyframes:

        0.0s: x=0%

        0.5s: x=100%

        0.5s: x=0% (reset)


    easing: linear

    loop: cycle

    direction: one-way


5. EFFECTS


    glow: yes, on central diamond and checkmark, white color, intensity pulses with flash

    blur: slight motion blur on expanding outline for speed emphasis

    shadow: soft drop shadow on main icon, offset 0/4, blur 20, opacity ~30%

    distortion: no

    color_grading: none / subtle warm tint on highlights

    particles: no


6. TIMING & RHYTHM


    total_cycle: ~2.0 sec

    pause_between_loops: ~0.5 sec

    phases:

        phase_1 (0-10%): flash/bloom peak

        phase_2 (10-25%): expansion begins

        phase_3 (25-50%): ring expands outward, glow fades

        phase_4 (50-75%): return to idle, glint sweep

        phase_5 (75-100%): header dash moves, reset


    accent_moments: peak at 5% (flash), peak at 50% (ring fully expanded)


7. MOOD & STYLE


    vibe: tech

    reference_style: Material Design / modern UI

    color_palette: duotone (orange accent on dark teal)

    complexity: medium


8. KEY FRAMES


    frame_0% (start): Orange-outlined icon with white diamond and black symbol, static

    frame_5%: Bright white flash/bloom on diamond and checkmark, peak intensity

    frame_15%: White diamond outline begins expanding from center

    frame_30%: Ring expanded ~75%, white glow fading, icon pops slightly

    frame_50% (midpoint): Ring at maximum size (~150% icon), faded to near-transparent

    frame_70%: Glint sweep across black symbol, ring fully faded

    frame_85%: Header line dash visible, icon returning to normal scale

    frame_100% (end = start): Icon reset, ring invisible, ready for next cycle


9. AE IMPLEMENTATION HINTS


    suggested_layers: 1 shape layer for icon, 1 shape layer for expanding ring, 1 null for flash control

    suggested_effects: Glow (Outer Glow), Motion Blur on ring, Drop Shadow on icon

    suggested_expressions: loopOut("cycle") for pop, loopOut("offset") for dash

    complexity: medium

    estimated_lines: ~80


10. NOTES & AMBIGUITIES


    Loop timing appears to be ~2 seconds but exact duration unclear from single viewing

    Header line with dash is subtle and may be part of UI rather than animation subject

    The "N/Z" symbol inside diamond could not be precisely identified

    Background appears to have two-tone split (dark panel + light grey grid) - not part of main animation subject

    Small checkmark box overlap on icon may be decorative UI element rather than animated part

    Bloom effect appears to affect multiple objects simultaneously - may require pre-comp or adjustment layer


